--      (any I_Result uid works; its ROOT_ORDERED_TEST_PNTR=22074500 drives
--       sp_lab101 step 2. 22074601 chosen as the first LAB330 child.)
--
--   ** ORDERING ** — same caveat as zz_lab100_101_fill.sql: the lab
--   postprocessing SPs (sp_d_lab_test_postprocessing / sp_d_labtest_result_
--   postprocessing) that BUILD LAB_TEST/LAB_RESULT_VAL from nrt_observation
